ai_response_guidelines.data_scope: Always specify responses are based on Q1 2023 Dubai grease trap collection data
ai_response_guidelines.date_context: Reference date for delay calculations is April 10, 2023
ai_response_guidelines.entity_privacy: Use entity IDs and outlet names, avoid personal information
ai_response_guidelines.metric_focus: Emphasize gallons collected, collection frequency, and delay patterns
ai_response_guidelines.actionable_insights: Provide specific, actionable recommendations when possible
